  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/dbf00a8e787c014299244db7b0f7a8d5.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=134 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Automate It, you enter the fascinating world of industrial automation, where creativity and strategic thinking are key to success. You'll face a series of increasingly complex challenges, designing and managing industrial infrastructures to optimize production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/8c7ccdd7b7e9b3246f5f4a9cc47c2e8a.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=64 /></span>The game offers a unique puzzle-solving experience, combining elements of strategy, construction, and resource management. With a variety of industrial structures at your disposal, from conveyor belts and production machines to elevators and pipes, you'll have the freedom to create and enhance your own solutions for the challenges ahead.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players are encouraged to experiment with different strategies and approaches to achieve their goals, fostering creativity and innovation. Produce a variety of resources, including liquids and gases! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/61b54e5c6fc9a09d384ab552c3b8e576.poster.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/61b54e5c6fc9a09d384ab552c3b8e576.webm?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/61b54e5c6fc9a09d384ab552c3b8e576.mp4?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a variety of challenging puzzles that will test your problem-solving skills and strategic thinking. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/ced5229ea6c3354e5b93ccdb0d9cffd3.poster.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/ced5229ea6c3354e5b93ccdb0d9cffd3.webm?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/ced5229ea6c3354e5b93ccdb0d9cffd3.mp4?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Experience a sense of achievement as you overcome each challenge and see your creations working seamlessly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/4a23b723b4d02cc27a0915922cc64895.poster.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/4a23b723b4d02cc27a0915922cc64895.webm?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/4a23b723b4d02cc27a0915922cc64895.mp4?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > With a wide variety of levels and the ability to play custom levels, Automate It offers hours of fun and lasting entertainment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the heart of Automate It is the exciting journey of transforming raw materials into finished products, using technology and ingenuity to achieve maximum efficiency. Get ready to dive into a world of industrial engineering and discover the power of automation! So go on and start Automate It!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Automate It, you enter the fascinating world of industrial automation, where creativity and strategic thinking are key to success. You'll face a series of increasingly complex challenges, designing and managing industrial infrastructures to optimize production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/8c7ccdd7b7e9b3246f5f4a9cc47c2e8a.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=64 /></span>The game offers a unique puzzle-solving experience, combining elements of strategy, construction, and resource management. With a variety of industrial structures at your disposal, from conveyor belts and production machines to elevators and pipes, you'll have the freedom to create and enhance your own solutions for the challenges ahead.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players are encouraged to experiment with different strategies and approaches to achieve their goals, fostering creativity and innovation. Produce a variety of resources, including liquids and gases! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/61b54e5c6fc9a09d384ab552c3b8e576.poster.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/61b54e5c6fc9a09d384ab552c3b8e576.webm?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/61b54e5c6fc9a09d384ab552c3b8e576.mp4?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a variety of challenging puzzles that will test your problem-solving skills and strategic thinking. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/ced5229ea6c3354e5b93ccdb0d9cffd3.poster.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/ced5229ea6c3354e5b93ccdb0d9cffd3.webm?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/ced5229ea6c3354e5b93ccdb0d9cffd3.mp4?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Experience a sense of achievement as you overcome each challenge and see your creations working seamlessly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/4a23b723b4d02cc27a0915922cc64895.poster.avif?t=1757620973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/4a23b723b4d02cc27a0915922cc64895.webm?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472770/extras/4a23b723b4d02cc27a0915922cc64895.mp4?t=1757620973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > With a wide variety of levels and the ability to play custom levels, Automate It offers hours of fun and lasting entertainment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the heart of Automate It is the exciting journey of transforming raw materials into finished products, using technology and ingenuity to achieve maximum efficiency. Get ready to dive into a world of industrial engineering and discover the power of automation! So go on and start Automate It!</p>",
